  "Description": {
    "English": "A metal 'egg' capsule, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to deploy!</span><br><br>A low hum resonates from deep within the capsule, its dissonant frequency turning the air around it a faint purple.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within is programmed to be <span class=\"name name-special\">free-spirited</span> and <span class=\"name name-special\">defiant</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一颗“卵”状金属胶囊，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">已可部署！</span><br><br>胶囊深处传来低沉的嗡嗡声，其不谐的频率让周围的空气都变成了淡紫色。<br><br>扫描显示，内里的生物已被编入<span class=\"name name-special\">奔放</span>与<span class=\"name name-special\">傲慢</span>的程序。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一個金屬「蛋」膠囊，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">即將部署！</span><br><br>膠囊深處傳來低沉的嗡嗡聲，其不和諧的頻率，將周圍的空氣變成了淡紫色。<br><br>掃描結果顯示，該生物經程序設計，具有以下形容地大小及特徵：<span class=\"name name-special\">自由奔放</span>且<span class=\"name name-special\">叛逆</span>。"
  },
